result.name: Tonkichi Tonkatsu Seafood

reviews.text: Japanese cuisine served with delicious Pork Cutlet and also in different kind of deep fried seafood such as oysters, shrimps. Ideal place for taking a glass of beer or sake to go with the deep fried tasty foods.

Still remember the days when there is always long queue outside every single Tonkichi restaurants in Hong Kong.   The food quality remains the same.   Crab Cream Croquette is my favourite and I also love the cutlet pork loin and oyster.
Excellent pork chop and refillable cabbage. Very good service as well. Lunch set more reasonable priced.
My favourite katsu Don. The royal king prawn is really giant and good!

It is one of the most famous pork cutlet restaurants. Prices starts HKD250, but I think the quality is not that same as years ago. Cabbage salad is coming along with main dish, which is refilled as long as you want. Environment is clean, modern, calm and tidy. People were very gentle and nice.

result.name: 丼吉日本吉列專門店餐廳

reviews.text: 人手不足，地方細小，卓子不足容納基本兩人餐之食物，食物質素並不特別，很是失望。

Japanese cuisine served with delicious Pork Cutlet and also in different kind of deep fried seafood such as oysters, shrimps. Ideal place for taking a glass of beer or sake to go with the deep fried tasty foods.

Still remember the days when there is always long queue outside every single Tonkichi restaurants in Hong Kong.   The food quality remains the same.   Crab Cream Croquette is my favourite and I also love the cutlet pork loin and oyster.

今日跟朋友去食好多人推薦的丼吉日式吉列豬扒專門店。
整個餐牌都吉列同吉列
當然是選擇豚肉
個人最喜歡這個，開胃又好吃。
必吃：吉列大蝦伴帶子定食
有兩顆帶子，三條蝦，份量一個人剛剛好。
其實帶子才是本體
帶子大顆到極點，內裡肉質又嫩又鮮甜。
蝦身彈牙得黎又易入口。
必吃：吉列京都銀雅豚
第一啖咬下去，豬肉味立即完全出來了，檔也檔不住，跟住肉汁都出來了。
真心好吃！再加上佢有少量肥肉，但一條根都吃唔到！
基本上一啖豚肉一啖白飯，一會兒就吃清光！
其實真做的不錯，但價格可以食秋葉原丸五兩次，仲可以開埋啤酒，就不得不要求高一點:1)肉量大，軟，但不夠肉汁，鬆林，但質偏瘦，不夠油香；2)米飯ok，但我是女性，也覺得量少；3)上菜的檸檬有很多核，擠一擠就會掉出來；4)盛載柚子汁的應該使用擠擠瓶或者壺；5)豬扒汁普通貨色，但盛載的壺倒汁后都會在壺嘴掛上一大滴，像貪吃貨在嘴角漏出汁液的鑱相；6) 白芝麻和黃芥末都不夠香。
